data.description: If you are looking for the perfect home with a wonderful location, don't look any further. This is a 3 bedroom 2 bathroom well laid out home, close to the the most important highways, shopping centers, and parks. Perfect for reunions and in a wonderful location .This home has a great open floor plan which makes it perfect for family gathering . The master bedroom and bathroom are spacious and very comforting. Also, enjoy the office/study with french doors that provide great privacy . This amazing home has an assumable VA loan at 6% if you qualify with the lender. Don't miss this great opportunity to call this place YOUR!
